trans-unit.source: Contains a strongly-typed collection of <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> objects.
Appends the specified <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> object to this collection.
The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> object to add to this collection.
The zero-based index of the added <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> object that is appended to this collection.
Appends the contents of the specified <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> array to this collection.
<xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> array that contains the objects to append to this collection.
Appends the contents of the specified <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntryCollection"></xref> object to this collection.
The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntryCollection"></xref> object that contains the objects to append to this collection.
Determines if the specified <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> object is in this collection.
The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> object to search for in this collection.
`true` if the specified <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> object is in this collection; otherwise, `false`.
Copies all <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> objects in this collection to the specified array, starting at the specified index in the target array.
The array of <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> objects that receives the elements of this collection.
The zero-based index in the array where this method starts copying this collection.
Returns the index of the first occurrence of the specified <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> object in this collection.
The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> object to search for in this collection.
The zero-based index of the first matching object.
Returns -1 if no member of this collection is identical to the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> object.
Inserts the specified <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> into this collection at the specified index.
The zero-based index in this collection where the object is inserted.
The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> object to insert into this collection.
Gets or sets a <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> object in this collection.
In C#, this property is the indexer for the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntryCollection> class.
In JScript, you can use the default indexed properties defined by a type, but you cannot explicitly define your own.
However, specifying the expando attribute on a class automatically provides a default indexed property with a type of Object and with an index type of <xref:System.String>.
The zero-based index of the <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> object to get or set.
The <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> object that exists at the specified index.
Overrides the <xref href="System.Collections.CollectionBase.OnClear"></xref> method.
Overrides the <xref href="System.Collections.CollectionBase.OnInsert(System.Int32,System.Object)"></xref> method.
The zero-based index at which to insert value.
The new value of the element at index.
Overrides the <xref href="System.Collections.CollectionBase.OnRemove(System.Int32,System.Object)"></xref> method.
The zero-based index at which value can be found.
The value of the element to remove from index.
Overrides the <xref href="System.Collections.CollectionBase.OnSet(System.Int32,System.Object,System.Object)"></xref> method.
The zero-based index at which oldValue can be found.
The value to replace with newValue.
The new value of the element at index.
Removes the first occurrence of an object in this collection that is identical to the specified <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> object.
The specified <xref href="System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryServicesPermissionEntry"></xref> object to remove from this collection.
